extends layout

block content
  div.col-xs-12.col-md-9.col-md-offset-1.mean-div
    div#icons-right.pull-right
      a(href='http://github.com/jmlevick/mean-boilerplate')
        i.fa.fa-github.fa-2x.topicons#githubicon
      a(href='http://twitter.com/Jmlevick')  
        i.fa.fa-twitter.fa-2x.topicons#twittericon
      a(href='http://jmlevick.tip.me/')  
        i.fa.fa-bitcoin.fa-2x.topicons#bitcoinicon
    if current_user == 'guest'
      div#userlog
        <span><i class="fa fa-user"></i> <b>#{current_user}</b> | <a class="myhref" href="/login">login</a></span>
    else
      div#userlog
        <span><i class="fa fa-user"></i> <b>#{current_user}</b> | <a href="/logout">logout</a></span>
    img(src='/img/expressjs.png', alt='Logo', id="logo")
    h1 Hello <span class="mean">{{guest.name}}</span>
    p This is a boilerplate app and you're @ <b>Homepage</b>
    .input-group.input-group-sm#demoinput
      input.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Your Name...', id="texti", ng-model="guest.name", ng-init="guest.name='MEAN'")
    hr
    h3 Getting started
    br
    ol.tips
      li Set up your database & Sessions Secret
      br
      | <b>Edit</b> <code>mongodb_uri</code> & <code>sessions_secret</code> @ <code>config/app.yaml</code>
      br
      br
      li Create a superuser for your project
      br
      | <b>Run</b> <code>npm run createadmin --admin="yourUsername" --password="yourPassword"</code>
      br
      br
      li Generate a scaffold
      br
      | <b>Run</b> <code>npm run scaffold --singular="post" --plural="posts"</code> (for example)
    br
    | After following these steps, please restart your project.
    br
    h3 Other useful npm tasks
    ol.tips
      li jscoffee
      | Live compiling of <b>.coffee</b> files to <b>minified .js</b>
      br
      br
      li coffeejs
      | Live compiling of <b>.coffee</b> files to <b>non-minified .js</b>
      br
      br
      li smushimg
      | Lossless compression for all the images used in your project via <b>Smushit!</b>
      br
      br
    h3 Project structure
    ol.tips
      li /
      | Root of the project. Contains <b>app.js</b>, <b>package.json</b>, <b>bower.json</b>, <b>Gemfile</b> among other important configuration files
      hr
      li /config
      | Contains <b>app.yaml</b>, scripts for the <b>scaffold generator</b>, the <b>admin creator</b> and whenever's <b>schedule.rb</b> file
      hr
      li /entities
      | Inside here, the scaffold generator creates a folder for each <b>entity</b> in your project. This entity folder contains the files <b>model.coffee</b> and <b>controller.coffee</b> for such entity
      hr
      li /extras
      | Miscelaneous <b>configuration files</b>, <b>middleware</b> and/or <b>custom modules</b> (passport, oatuh, etc)
      hr
      li /log
      | All logs go here. <b>Cron's</b> autogenerated log (via whenever) gets saved to this folder
      hr
      li /public
      | All <b>assets</b> go here, it has a special folder for <b>bower</b> installed components
      hr
      li /routes.coffee
      | Your project's <b>general routes</b> are declared here
      hr
      li /scaffolds
      | Where the <b>base templates</b> for the <b>scaffold generator</b> are taken from
      hr
      li /scripts
      | Folder for <b>random scripts</b> you might need to include (<b>DevOps tasks</b> for example)
      hr
      li /views
      | The <b>views</b> for your entities and your project overall... This folder includes <b>layouts</b> and <b>partials</b>
